15 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
16 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
17 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 5-142.2 of Title 70, unless
18 there is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
19 A. Except as otherwise provided in subsection D of this
20 section, beginning with the 2025-2026 school year, a school district
21 board of education and the governing body of a charter school shall
22 request that the Oklahoma State Bureau of Investigation (OSBI)
23 provide a national criminal history record check for a volunteer
24 prior to the individual volunteering at a school district or charter
